  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improved Public Services in Sisian and Alaverdi ADPs through Citizen Empowerment</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is designed to tackle the root causes of the lack of, or insufficient access to, good quality public services across 20 communities within 2 of the WV Armenia Area Development Programmes.  The project aims to; a)&#xA0;further promote community participation and the delivery of basic services; b) further strengthen the capacity of local authorities to accept and promote civil society participation in decision making, implementing and monitoring processes;  c) further build the capacity of the community and civil society to participate in these processes.</narrative>
  </description>
